WEBVTT

00:08.000 --> 00:10.709
[Ray] Previously
on  Ray Donovan...

00:10.709 --> 00:12.291
I know who did it.

00:12.291 --> 00:14.041
And I know how much
you paid them.

00:14.041 --> 00:16.083
The studio and the network.

00:16.083 --> 00:20.125
Doug and I had a deal.
We had an understanding.

00:20.125 --> 00:22.625
So what do you want
from me?

00:22.625 --> 00:24.291
- I want you to kill him.
- Fuck you.

00:24.291 --> 00:26.709
Natalie James walked off
the set two days ago.

00:26.709 --> 00:28.834
I need you to find her.

00:28.834 --> 00:31.667
I'm pregnant.
It's Doug's.

00:31.667 --> 00:33.500
And he told me
to get an abortion.

00:33.500 --> 00:35.959
♪ dramatic music ♪

00:35.959 --> 00:37.667
♪♪♪

00:37.667 --> 00:39.917
I slept with someone.

00:39.917 --> 00:41.709
You what?

00:41.709 --> 00:44.083
[crying] I'm sorry.
I'm so sorry.

00:45.208 --> 00:47.208
[Terry] You left the boy
when he was 13,

00:47.208 --> 00:49.709
and now he's got a chance
at the big-time,

00:49.709 --> 00:51.250
you're coming
out the woodwork.

00:51.250 --> 00:54.125
- I'm his father.
- Can we just have him

00:54.125 --> 00:55.709
be part of the team, Ter?

00:55.709 --> 00:57.709
If he's in, I'm out.

00:57.709 --> 00:59.083
And all the money in this
place here, too, that's out.

00:59.083 --> 01:00.750
That surgery
was brutal, wasn't it?

01:00.750 --> 01:02.959
I never got the surgery.

01:02.959 --> 01:05.291
- You're in remission.
- Yeah.

01:05.291 --> 01:06.500
So it worked.

01:06.500 --> 01:08.041
Jake Smith is my boyfriend.

01:08.041 --> 01:10.000
- How's he doing?
- He's dying!

01:10.000 --> 01:12.875
You have to help him.

01:12.875 --> 01:14.333
[Ray] I was hoping
you could talk to the D.A.,

01:14.333 --> 01:15.291
maybe get him
to drop the charges

01:15.291 --> 01:17.542
- against my daughter.
- Absolutely not.

01:17.542 --> 01:18.166
I'm gonna need you
to put your hands

01:18.166 --> 01:20.208
behind your back, Mick.

01:20.208 --> 01:22.041
- What are you doin', Frank?
- You fuck!

01:22.041 --> 01:23.542
Sing this, fucker!

01:23.542 --> 01:24.917
- [gunshot]
- [Mickey] Asshole!

01:25.834 --> 01:28.875
You killed him.
He's the head of the FBI.

01:28.875 --> 01:30.583
[Ray] I can tell you
where the body is,

01:30.583 --> 01:31.917
and I can tell you
who killed him.

01:31.917 --> 01:33.709
My daughter got arrested.

01:33.709 --> 01:35.667
I need the charges
dropped.

01:35.667 --> 01:37.917
Tell me who did it...
I'll let your daughter out.

01:37.917 --> 01:41.250
I'm gonna need
a murder weapon, Ray.

01:41.250 --> 01:42.917
- [Linda] Aah!
- [Mickey] What the fuck?

01:42.917 --> 01:44.250
- [man] Let's go!
- What's the charge,

01:44.250 --> 01:45.583
you assholes?

01:45.583 --> 01:46.750
This is a country
of fuckin' laws!

01:46.750 --> 01:48.041
You gave 'em Mick.

01:48.041 --> 01:49.583
Where's the gun, Daryll?

01:49.583 --> 01:51.041
I ain't found it yet.

01:51.041 --> 01:53.166
♪ dramatic music ♪

01:53.166 --> 01:55.166
Did you send Barnes
to arrest me?

01:55.166 --> 01:56.959
Of course I did.

01:56.959 --> 01:59.125
You fucked me
for the last time.

01:59.125 --> 02:00.333
I'm gonna get you, Raymond.

02:10.917 --> 02:14.750
♪ somber piano notes ♪

02:14.750 --> 02:19.875
♪♪♪

02:33.792 --> 02:35.875
