03:30.709 --> 03:34.875
[pastor] The Lord is good
to those who wait for Him.

03:34.875 --> 03:37.667
We anticipate the day

03:37.667 --> 03:39.792
- ♪ Ah ah ah ah...♪
- When spirit and body

03:39.792 --> 03:42.208
are united again
at the coming of the Lord,

03:42.208 --> 03:45.166
and we find great comfort
in knowing

03:45.166 --> 03:48.208
that we shall forever
be together with the Lord,

03:48.208 --> 03:50.000
and whoever
is united with the Lord

03:50.000 --> 03:53.125
is one with Him in spirit.

03:53.125 --> 03:57.083
Although He causes grief,

03:57.083 --> 03:58.417
the Lord will have
compassion...

03:58.417 --> 04:03.583
according to the abundance
of His steadfast love...

04:03.583 --> 04:07.709
for He does not willingly
afflict or aggrieve anyone.

04:07.709 --> 04:08.792
Do not let your hearts
be troubled.

04:08.792 --> 04:11.041
Believe in God.

04:11.041 --> 04:13.750
Believe also in me.

04:13.750 --> 04:15.583
In my Father's house...

04:15.583 --> 04:20.458
